{"tid":1226890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日會去遊行既入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-15T13:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:38:44.000Z","uid":156766,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b2a6495ee1cc48e07214a03d94be3248fa4803","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"想同大家講 聽日一定一定要做和理非 <br />\n依加係打民意戰 如果聽日勇武的話 會令偏向反送中既和理非失去信心 更加俾對家有位入我地<br />\n要勇武再擇日 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日一定要做和理非</span>"},{"pid":"82eb654a29c58d46bcd74f849379d60dcca7a37a","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:45:32.000Z","msg":"Push push push"},{"pid":"c8285503faaf2c1544571f8773fafa13ba2b7b9c","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"66a715775e7115d2bd50c496608b22c9b7828246","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"430d0696546c3299b914193993b93f9a008c820a","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"fbab2a31505fd1ded378eb925c21f74881235a72","tid":1226890,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:47:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港政府，血債血償</span></span>"},{"pid":"1c3769b86cf41d3a1d580a97c8078fa8cda2e5ca","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:47:26.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"068989f03133efa1f482be3caff11ea001d6069c","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日大家要小心有鬼！！！！</span>"},{"pid":"7863190df9e14e2987d0922206ff60584c99b451","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-