水咁耐係時後上水啦，我地唔介意你地攞盡光環，希望你地唔好枉費我地義士o既付出。今次幫你捉埋鹿，識唔識脫角就睇你地。係議會入面o既角色靠曬你地，我地已經做盡。<br />\n<br />\n推到泛民做野！！！"},{"pid":"264f8491dc60e705ef9adc47673d02c4891a71ee","tid":1226890,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>邊撚個有鬼呀又分化 食撚咗屎？</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3c15c367c7730a398f13e6eeecec4bb985bbcdca","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"264f8491dc60e705ef9adc47673d02c4891a71ee","tid":1226890,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>邊撚個有鬼呀又分化 食撚咗屎？</strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"唔撚係分化阿屌 我既意思係警犬混係遊行到做鬼"},{"pid":"23d5a4310cdf8e03c33dc8eb766d90029911c43d","tid":1226890,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c15c367c7730a398f13e6eeecec4bb985bbcdca","tid":1226890,"uid":156766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"264f8491dc60e705ef9adc47673d02c4891a71ee","tid":1226890,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>邊撚個有鬼呀又分化 食撚咗屎？</strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"唔撚係分化阿屌 我既意思係警犬混係遊行到做鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"咁鐘意捉鬼自己捉飽佢"}]}